title: Looking For Duo!
body:
Looking for Gold 4 + 
Hi i am looking for a good duo partner, we will help each other ladder to diamond + is currently Gold 2 now. Must play SOLO Lanes and is good at what they do.
i have skype and working mic, can play any rolls, flexible!
Non-Toxic and doesn't blame people on same team so they rage quit, just play to win (well usually the toxicity happens when the team is losing lolz)
Normally on 5~9pm 

Feel free to add!
